{
  "stem": "4695.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But my wife tells me, no.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "In [?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Lanberg, ?] we have companions.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Again, people who run from Lodz.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We have the friends and the companions and the-- the clubs.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we have a nice living.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Why to go away?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I tell her, listen.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Here is a war.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And then I explained, listen, Lanka, I know here will be, if the Germans will attack, it's not only the Germans will kill you.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "The Ukrainians will kill you, too.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Then I think not one Jewish man can be saved on this territory because I must look at it like that.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And she tell me, here is the Russian Army.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I tell, listen, I saw the German Army.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I saw the Russian Army.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "The Russian Army cannot keep the front.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Maybe they will keep because the distance, the time, the winter, and they have time to organize fresh armies from Siberia, from [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "But in beginning, I tell her, the Russian will not get the front.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "They must back-- step back, back and back.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And if you like to stay, listen to me, you know me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "I know Ukrainian.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "I could be saved.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "But I will not let you, as a pregnant woman, for the Germans to die.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And I will say, if you like, I will be dead because you do not understand this situation.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "It's up to you.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Then you take my life in your hand.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "Then she start crying.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "Tell, OK, let's go.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And we go to the city Stalinabad, in middle Asia.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "This is not far between Iran and China, you know, very far away.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, we were-- I go-- these are the-- how is that-- organized workers who specialists to Asia.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I, with my own sign--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Volunteered with my wife to go there.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
